- `@utils/*` → `src/libs/utils/*`
- `@communication/*` → `src/libs/communication/*`
- `@database/*` → `src/libs/infrastructure/database/*`
- `@config` → `src/config`
- `@logging` → `src/libs/infrastructure/logging`
